features: 【Adjustable & Foldable】The laptop stand can raise your laptop up to 7.48 inches. You can incline at different angles and stand it up higher or lower depending on your needs, which will be extremely convenient if you use your laptop in a variety of position. In addition, it is foldable for easy storage and easy to carry.

【Stable & Sturdy】With quality aluminum alloy material, the adjustable laptop stand is more sturdy and durable. It can support up to 8.8 lbs (4 kg) without shaking the panel. The panel and its two hooks are designed with non-slip straps to make the laptop riser more stable, and 4 non-slip silicone pads at the bottom help prevent the computer riser from sliding. These considerate designs are to ensure you better use.
【Cooling & Ventilation】The laptop holder only has two holder hands but not a whole flat, so there is more space to enable the heat to vent and keep your laptop from overheating.

【Muti-Use & Practical】Multi-use in many occasions such as offices, meeting rooms, living room, kitchens and other occasions to hold the laptops. At the same time, the bottom storage slot can store small items such as mobile phones, keys, etc. An excellent gift for your friends and family!

【Wide Compatibility】Compatible with all laptops 10 to 16 inches, and compatible with MacBook/ MacBook Air/ MacBook Pro/ Microsoft Surface/HP/ Dell/ Google laptops up to 16 inches, etc. In addition, this is also a great choice as a Christmas gift and a New Year gift for family and friends!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works perfectly, small footprint, and great price!
reviews.reviewText: This is my second laptop stand. My prior one had a fan built in that I did not need, but was not great at adjusting. This one is design perfection. It take a little effort to position, but holds the position well. The base takes up a small footprint on my desk and allows me to use the laptop screen as a dual monitor. I've already had one coworker ask where I got it from and I sent them a link to order it. Probably the best thing I've ordered on Amazon in the last couple months.

reviews.reviewText: The stand was very easy to use right out of the box. It’s adjustable in a few ways for the right height and angle It just seems to be slightly off level, but I think I can fix that pretty easily. Overall a very good product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for travel
reviews.reviewText: I have a standing desk and am used to switching often from sitting to standing. When I travel, I take this stand with me because I am to work at any desk and still get to stand or sit if needed. It is a pain in the butt to adjust, it's tough to fold, but once in place, it is very sturdy. When I am not traveling, I have it on my desk as a third screen and adjust it to the perfect height for video calls. great addition to your office set up if you work off a laptop.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great stand at a great price!
reviews.reviewText: It's light and sturdy; I'm already considering buying one for my wife's desk.I used to use books to raise my laptop, but this takes it to another level (literally!). It's robust, and securely holds both my work computer and my 14" MacBook without any issues. Initially, I thought I had to unscrew something on the stand to move it, but later I realized that you need to apply some force to move it. In my opinion, it's not the type of base you adjust every two to three hours; it's more the kind you set and leave, maybe moving it once or twice a week.I would definitely recommend it to my friends and purchase it again for my family.
